{"title": "Modbus", "source": "hardware-att", "source_label": "HardwareAllTheThings", "path": "protocols/modbus", "html": "<h1 id=\"modbus\">Modbus</h1>\n<h2 id=\"discovery\">Discovery</h2>\n<p><strong>Modbus Client:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/qmodbus/\">QModBus</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/riptideio/pymodbus\">pymodbus</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.modbustools.com/\">Modbus Tools</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Modbus Discover Nmap Script:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script<span class=\"w\"> </span>modbus-discover.nse<span class=\"w\"> </span>--script-args<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;modbus-discover.aggressive=true&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">502</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;host&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Connect to Modbus Slave:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">pymodbus.client</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">ModbusTcpClient</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">client</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">ModbusTcpClient</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;IP_Address_of_Target&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">client</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">write_coil</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">result</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">client</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">read_coils</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">result</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">bits</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">])</span>\n<span class=\"n\">client</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">close</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Modbus Pentesting:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/0x0mar/smod\">smod</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"modbus-simulators\">Modbus Simulators</h2>\n<p><strong>Modbus Slave Simulator</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.modbusdriver.com/diagslave.html\">Diagslave</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modbuspal.sourceforge.net/\">ModbusPal</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Modbus Master Simulator</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.modbusdriver.com/modpoll.html\">modpoll</a></li>\n</ul>", "excerpt": "Modbus Discovery Modbus Client: QModBus pymodbus Modbus Tools Modbus Discover Nmap Script: nmap --script modbus-discover.nse --script-args = &#39;modbus-discover.aggressive=true&#39; -p 502 &lt;host&gt; Connect to Modbus Slave: from pymodbus.client…", "tags": []}